ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Consenting to the Amendments to the Tsawwassen First Nation Final Agreement
PrecisOrder consenting to the amendments to the TSAWWASSEN FIRST NATION FINAL AGREEMENT in order to (1) reinstate the application of the tax exemption on the portion of Tsawwassen Lands that were formerly reserve lands prior to the Tsawwassen First Nation Final Agreement coming into effect; and (2) reinstate the application of the tax exemption to Tsawwassen Members who are registered under the Act.
